SPELL NAME  : Cause serious wounds
SPELL SYNTAX: -Csw <target>
SPELL COST  : 27 SP
DESCRIPTION : The devote cleric has the power to call upon the power of Mitra
	      for to inflict damage, as well as to heal it. By force of will
	      and through the cleric's devotion, Mitra will inflict serious
	      wounds upon the target of her wrath.
